snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls: Legends - E3 2018 Official Trailer
snippet.description:
We’re excited to show you the all-new Legends, coming soon!

There’s no reason to wait - download anywhere and play now!

ESRB RATING: TEEN with Violence and Blood.
